Class Exercise

  • java.lang.Object
    • teameleven.smartbells2.businesslayer.tableclasses.Exercise

  • public class Exercise
extends java.lang.Object
    Base Exercise Class. Describes a Single Exercise, including the number of reps and sets in a basic performance of the exercise. portion of the SmartBells Project, created by Team Eleven. Edits Updated to match API fields AR Oct 21, 2015
